com.Netzwerk.de

Class Model

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.Netzwerk.de.Model

  • public class Model
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describe a object that stores all the relevant values for the server
    - maximum Limit
    - XML file path
    - XSD file path
    - Database XML file path
    - Database XSD file path
    - Strategy algorithm
    - The advanced client option
    - The config path
    - The server port
    - The administration server port
    Version:
    0.0.1
